CustomField.description: Controls the pixel width for Project/Assignment dropdown on Timecard Entry UI. Please specify a whole number for this value, as this will directly go into width. For ex a value 300 will set the dropdown width to 300px.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Controls the pixel width for Project/Assignment dropdown on Timecard Entry UI. Please specify a whole number for this value, as this will directly go into width. For ex a value 300 will set the dropdown width to 300px.
CustomField.label: Width px for project assig drop down
